   "source": [
    "# 🌋 Thalia — Local Training on M4 Mac\n",
    "\n",
    "## Key insight from their source code:\n",
    "```\n",
    "image.pth shape: [9, 512, 512]\n",
    "             =  [T * C, H, W]\n",
    "             =  [3 timesteps × 3 channels, 512, 512]\n",
    "```\n",
    "The paper stacks time as channels. Your LSTM will process them as a real sequence.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "⚠️ Run from inside your `volcano-thesis/` directory with `volcano` env activated."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Cell 1 — Check MPS device (Apple Silicon GPU)"
